issues.message:
Android Build Tools 24.0.0 are too new and may or may not work with Titanium.
If you encounter problems, select a supported version with:
   __ti config android.buildTools.selectedVersion ##.##.##__
 where ##.##.## is a version in /Users/MarcoDuff/Library/android-sdk-macosx/build-tools that is 23.x
